description: F.B.I. Detective Stories - June 1949 [vol1 No3] English | 132 pages | PDF | 17.1 mb F.B.I. Detective Stories was a short-lived Popular publication that began life in February 1949 and ran for 14 bi-monthly issues. As one might assume, all of the stories included in the magazine feature either FBI agents or ex-FBI agents. PDF made by me with OCR & bookmarks but scan is not mine.
